; HMBC Batch 1 -- 4 correlations (HMBC 9 10 replaced by grouped (8 9) 10 in batch 2)
HMBC 3 13        ; C3(136.96) <- H13(1.50): alpha-Me to aromat. ipso para (3J: H13-C13-C7-C3)
HMBC 1 9         ; C1(180.56) <- H9(3.71):  alpha-CH to COOH carbonyl (3J)
